Floor plan: natural-flow sidebars, blank canvas on first load

1) Right-hand sidebar (Stats & Presets / Your Selections / Layout Preset)
   no longer scrolls internally. The shared FloorPlanSidebar drops its
   max-h-[calc(100vh-5rem)] + overflow-y-auto cap and its sticky
   positioning so the column extends as tall as its children require
   inside the natural page flow. The QA Desk panel sheds its inner
   max-h-64 + overflow-y-auto so findings list naturally as well.

2) The Step 3 Floor Plan canvas now defaults to a blank shell. The
   timeout-driven auto-populate effect that ran on first entry is
   removed; the populatePlaceholdersRef is still passed to the planner
   so the explicit Populate Generic Placeholders / Auto-plan buttons
   inside the workspace continue to work.
